{"tid":166020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街，屋企有老鼠","createTime":"2017-03-21T18:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T11:00:02.000Z","uid":14291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df8c962b62b51ee48449cc1602406cc9f7055d16","tid":166020,"uid":14291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:56:03.000Z","msg":"老豆話屋企有隻手掌咁大嘅老鼠周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又食曬我啲公仔麵，初頭我都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企住2x樓邊可能有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但正話出廳去廁所個陣，比野撞親隻腳邊，我嚇到尿都唔敢屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返房開燈一睇，撞個位真係有兩條爪痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfa38d7a10131fcbbbc054e1c9192f6807d5695","tid":166020,"uid":86476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:57:14.000Z","msg":"2x幾樓都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7484b4a1b9d474288d7baecc689539ed97321c07","tid":166020,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:57:18.000Z","msg":"可能係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04234f9e546b8f18da69c87eea4bad9399542e47","tid":166020,"uid":74289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T18:58:31.000Z","msg":"都幾嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3845bbc56cecc1a22aa689475a461aa6cd4cf2","ti